cast.overview: Vincent is an all-too-human man who dares to defy a system obsessed with genetic perfection. He is an "In-Valid" who assumes the identity of a member of the genetic elite to pursue his goal of traveling into space with the Gattaca Aerospace Corporation.
cast.title: Gattaca

details.biography: Susan Jennifer Grace Sullivan is known for Gattaca (1997), Friday the 13th Part VII: The New Blood (1988), Click: The Calendar Girl Killer (1990), and Charles in Charge (1984). She was married to director Andrew Niccol from 1991 until their divorce in 2002. She is a cancer survivor and still lives in California. In 2012, the Crystal Lake Memories documentary mistakenly reported about her passing by confusing her with a woman of a similar name.
details.name: Susan Jennifer Sullivan
